<br />

<br />
It says bards should be able to solo.  I cannot function outside of a group (which is the only reason I got as far as I did).  But I can't always find groups when I want to play.  And I <b>can't</b> solo.  I can barely kill things light blue to me, which take up half my health, and give almost no experience.  And dark blue is right out.  I chicken out and run before I get close to killing them.
<br />

<br />
What am I doing wrong? (Everything.)  I get bashed too much, and lose my song.  Is that normal or just a low-level thing? I have only the area damage spell which I <b>can't</b> use because I'll have five things hitting me at once.  I know I have to work on my weapon skill but it only seems to go up once per game session, as I've noticed.
<br />

<br />
This is frustrating and near impossible.  I'm tempted to scrap this character... Help?</span></td>
