				<td colspan="2"><span>most noob zones have snakes in them or spider. 
<br />
Kill them collect there eggs and silks. these sell in bazaar easily at 1 plat a piece.
<br />

<br />
or open a 7-11 
<br />
Hit Freeport and get Fuzzle cutter 5000. Sell in bazaar at 1 plat each.
<br />

<br />
Trust me they will sell. Its a convienece. Get some food to if you can. People don't wanna hunt down the food vendors or waste there stat foods.
<br />

<br />
A few hundred plat is easy to get. Its what you do with it that counts.
<br />

<br />
Fast low damage weapons are like 5-50plat in the bazaar. don't look for stats yet anyways. A sharpend floatsom is nice for skill ups once you hit 27 tho.
<br />

<br />
Twisting is a nesesity for a bard but with socials, hotbuttons, and the melody comand its cake.
<br />

<br />
Make a few socials.
<br />
Melee
<br />
/melody 1 2 3   (the # corespond to your spell gems. so 1 should be hymn, 2 should be Jonathons, and 3 should be Chords 
<br />

<br />
Kiting isn't really an option for ya you can kinda meele kit something. Go in and melee a mob, If it starts to get the upper hand  run around it twisting/melody ing it with selos and bellows once you get it.
<br />

<br />
Later on you can Selos, fear, chain kite stuff,
<br />
Then charm kite stuff
<br />
then chant kite.
<br />

<br />
Basically check out the Guides section for info on all of this
<br />

<br />
Rao
<br />

